        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Climate Justice Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill requires the President to establish a Climate Justice Working Group that must advise federal entities on a just and equitable transition towards a clean, climate-resilient, and zero-emission economy.</p>]]>
        </text>
